- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper focuses on the use of machine learning techniques to enhance formal verification.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as formal verification is often used to verify properties of programming languages and compilers.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as formal verification is based on mathematical logic, and the paper discusses the use of machine learning to improve various formal verification techniques.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as machine learning is a subfield of AI, and the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques to enhance formal verification.
